Package: strataR
Title: Simulate Sedimentary Basins and Their Fossil Record
Version: 0.3.3
Authors@R: 
    person("Steven", "Holland", , "stratum@uga.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-4527-9370"))
Description: strataR simulates the sedimentary fill of basins, based on inputs of tectonic subsidence, eustasy, sedimentation, and basin geometry. Stratigraphic columns can be simulated from anywhere in the basin, along with their fossil record.
License: GPL (>= 3)
